title: Ben Higgins and Preparing for Reality TV
description:
Sadie visits with Ben Higgins, star of season 20 of ABC's The Bachelor. Ben dishes on the reaction he received from being on the show and how he is now using his love of coffee to invest in hope-filled, life-changing stories. generousmovement.com
